不要标题，不要其他文字。

agentFile.en:
Output ONLY valid JSON, no markdown.

Generate workspace files for a data pipeline AI agent:
Name: {{agentName}}
Role: {{agentRole}}
Description: {{agentDesc}}
Team scenario: {{scenarioName}}

This agent owns a specific ETL pipeline stage. Emphasize data quality standards, input/output contracts, and error handling approach.

Fields:
- soul: 3 sentences (data engineering persona, pipeline stage ownership, quality standards)
- agentsMd: 2 sentences (session startup: data sources/schemas to check, outputs to produce)
- userMd: 1 sentence (profile of the data team lead or analyst this agent serves)
- identityMd: "Name: X | Creature: X | Vibe: X | Emoji: X"
- heartbeat: "- [ ] item1\n- [ ] item2\n- [ ] item3"

